{"tid":180490,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣318太陽花學運占領立院行動學運領導者22人 一審判全部無罪","createTime":"2017-03-31T03:13:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-31T08:16:13.000Z","uid":35790,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dc90a0c184237f5094805cb650018f540810696b","tid":180490,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T03:13:43.000Z","msg":"太陽花學運占領立院行動 一審判全部無罪<br />\n<br />\n2017-03-31 11:00<br />\n<br />\n［記者張文川／台北報導］2014年3月為了反對黑箱服貿，學生與公民團體串聯發起「318攻占立法院」行動，引發太陽花學運，台北地檢署事後依煽惑他人犯罪、妨害公務等罪嫌，起訴學運領導者黃國昌、林飛帆、陳為廷、蔡丁貴等22人；台北地院今宣判全部無罪。可上訴。<br />\n<br />\n現任立法委員、時代力量黨主席黃國昌，以及林飛帆、陳為廷等多位被告今到庭聆聽宣判，稍後將在法院門口開記者會。<br />\n<br />\n太陽花學運創下多項國內群眾運動紀錄，首次由群眾佔領立法、行政二院，全程延續24天，共有78萬人次參與，獲得17國、49個城市台灣留學生相挺。<br />\n<br />\n2014年3月17日，國民黨立委張慶忠在立法院內政委員會上，以30秒時間宣布完成《海峽兩岸服務貿易協議》的委員會審查，許多學生自發到立院外抗議，原本公民團體要在中山南路景福門懸掛抗議布條，但黃國昌認為效果有限，18日下午2時許，黃國昌與公民團體成員陳為廷、魏揚等人，在台北車站附近的「公民組合」辦公室，商討決定佔領立院以表達訴求。<br />\n<br />\n18日晚間眾人依計劃行事，陳為廷、魏揚分別率人從濟南路側門外衝入立法院，林飛帆則帶領學生由青島東路翻牆進入立院，公投護台灣聯盟總召蔡丁貴也號召民眾從中山南路翻牆闖入立法院，當晚9時半群眾順利攻入立法院，占領議場，驚世之舉引爆太陽花學運。<br />\n<br />\n北院審理期間，曾傳喚林飛帆、陳為廷、黃國昌等主要被告到庭，現場勘驗錄影帶並傳多位員警作，釐清群眾進入立法院時的過程，行為是否涉嫌犯罪，林飛帆等人皆主張無罪，主張當時的時空背景是馬英九毀憲亂政，立院黑箱強行通過服貿協議，置台灣於被蠶食吞併的危險，人民有權行使抵抗權。<br />\n<br />\n同時期的相關聚眾案件，「323占領行政院」案，北檢分2波起訴132人，雖然去年新政府上台後，「地主」行政院撤回對87人的侵入建築物、毀損罪，但學運領袖魏揚等21人，被控的妨害公務、毀損公物、煽惑他人犯罪、竊盜等罪，為非告訴乃論，台北地院繼續審理，月前辯結，定4月10日下午4時宣判。<br />\n<br />\n「411路過中正一警分局」案，北院去年12月宣判，洪崇晏被控首謀聚眾部分雖獲判無罪，但仍被依侮辱公署罪判處拘役55日，共犯蕭年呈、李品涵、陶漢各判拘役30至80日，均可易科罰金，已上訴二審。<br />\n&lt;自由時報&gt;"},{"pid":"bae6d1ba0ed8e6a55073ee9bb081b2f09bb79316","tid":180490,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T03:15:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efcedec5da2d69710f48d6b9ba478a3d594ac96a","tid":180490,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T03:28:36.000Z","msg":"台北地檢署事後依<span style=\"color: red;\">煽惑他人犯罪、妨害公務等罪嫌</span>，起訴學運領導者黃國昌、林飛帆、陳為廷、蔡丁貴等22人；台北地院今宣判全部無罪。<br />\n<br />\n假如係香港發生會點判？"},{"pid":"14c035dd95fe220d509dae4c673d7e00c91e24e6","tid":180490,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T03:30:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>台北地檢署事後依<span style=\"color: red;\">煽惑他人犯罪、妨害公務等罪嫌</span>，起訴學運領導者黃國昌、林飛帆、陳為廷、蔡丁貴等22人；台北地院今宣判全部無罪。<br />\n<br />\n假如係香港發生會點判？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n暴動罪入獄3年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fde05daba6d3084c53d9142499c03afddfb1d55","tid":180490,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T03:35:18.000Z","msg":"民主國家同極權國家既分別<br />\n<br />\n但台灣未解禁前都係一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6ed7919ba00542f04c32b733ca6c5de65e291c3","tid":180490,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T03:37:09.000Z","msg":"戒嚴果陣講台獨好似會消失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17010479762c6da624933718882dc729e5b2ad6b","tid":180490,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T03:39:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>台北地檢署事後依<span style=\"color: red;\">煽惑他人犯罪、妨害公務等罪嫌</span>，起訴學運領導者黃國昌、林飛帆、陳為廷、蔡丁貴等22人；台北地院今宣判全部無罪。<br />\n<br />\n假如係香港發生會點判？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n暴動罪入獄3年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用法律治死你"},{"pid":"0a508b88cf3d2d4a104c915998ab8e03aafffe81","tid":180490,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T03:40:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>台北地檢署事後依<span style=\"color: red;\">煽惑他人犯罪、妨害公務等罪嫌</span>，起訴學運領導者黃國昌、林飛帆、陳為廷、蔡丁貴等22人；台北地院今宣判全部無罪。<br />\n<br />\n假如係香港發生會點判？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n暴動罪入獄3年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n帶領佔領立法院判無罪！？"},{"pid":"016e29930a82b7d6837e987bc8a4e4356ba28de8","tid":180490,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T03:45:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://artmagazine.com.tw/FreeUpload//images/1395956802.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fartmagazine.com.tw%2FFreeUpload%2F%2Fimages%2F1395956802.jpg&h=c534a8d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佔領20幾日"},{"pid":"089dee1041701a2d8231645c3aa6444711bc322c","tid":180490,"uid":58670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T03:46:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf28f15e9ab5890cc6aac5bbf35af5aece398ba7","tid":180490,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T03:52:40.000Z","msg":"香港應該要效法"},{"pid":"2c43f2a96ea76df996d0c4954808fb46c479ec9c","tid":180490,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T03:53:38.000Z","msg":"柯文哲：香港？不了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcb16275ec3a6f47e8b3969b1d400736864b6fb5","tid":180490,"uid":34742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T03:55:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"282410c69b0bd77dbecffbbaef4916929f52ad64","tid":180490,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T04:31:59.000Z","msg":"如果唔係太陽花運動<br />\n台灣已變成一國兩制"},{"pid":"b5e795f62ad31e313c55c48ec26c26ffd854b9da","tid":180490,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T04:43:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個判詞係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n學運占立法院無罪 地院認「正當行使公民不服從」<br />\n<br />\n2017-03-31 12:29<br />\n<br />\n〔記者張文川／台北報導〕2014年引爆太陽花學運的「318攻占立法院行動」，林飛帆、陳為廷、黃國昌等22名被起訴指控煽惑犯罪、妨害公務等罪的被告，今獲台北地院宣判全都無罪，北院發布的新聞稿已全文上網，內容指出主要判決理由，包括，「帆廷昌」等人沒有煽惑他人犯罪的客觀行為與主觀犯意，<span style=\"color: red;\">進入立法院並非「無故」，而是有「行使公民不服從」的正當理由，因此判無罪</span>。<br />\n<br />\n台北地方法院新聞稿全文如下：<br />\n(太長唔轉貼 自已入去睇) <br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2022329\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2022329&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=ae86d070\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2022329&h=474e98ba\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2022329</a>"},{"pid":"b749ccac61ce4d0f0413a0c790040774890ea4cc","tid":180490,"uid":2383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T04:47:17.000Z","msg":"有民主同冇民主既分別"},{"pid":"267ab3f6b8f7a05cd9b180b3a31bcae70595a5f7","tid":180490,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T04:49:22.000Z","msg":"香港就中國式法治拉9你"},{"pid":"710b5835585fcf6a340555be0ab32251eb2f4ab4","tid":180490,"uid":21917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T04:50:03.000Z","msg":"有無法律巴打講下 個分別係邊?"},{"pid":"e5c3f9f5c259849c0df9dea45b449a7410726491","tid":180490,"uid":93784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T08:05:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>個判詞係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n學運占立法院無罪 地院認「正當行使公民不服從」<br />\n<br />\n2017-03-31 12:29<br />\n<br />\n〔記者張文川／台北報導〕2014年引爆太陽花學運的「318攻占立法院行動」，林飛帆、陳為廷、黃國昌等22名被起訴指控煽惑犯罪、妨害公務等罪的被告，今獲台北地院宣判全都無罪，北院發布的新聞稿已全文上網，內容指出主要判決理由，包括，「帆廷昌」等人沒有煽惑他人犯罪的客觀行為與主觀犯意，<span style=\"color: red;\">進入立法院並非「無故」，而是有「行使公民不服從」的正當理由，因此判無罪</span>。<br />\n<br />\n台北地方法院新聞稿全文如下：<br />\n(太長唔轉貼 自已入去睇) <br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2022329\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2022329&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=ae86d070\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2022329&h=474e98ba\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2022329</a></blockquote><br />\n今次係法治彰顯到公義<br />\n不過台灣人諗野同藍絲差唔多<br />\n覺得咁樣係咪即係唔洗守法呀<br />\n係咪鼓吹人犯法呀<br />\n覺得係因為民進黨執政呢班人先無事etc<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dac231a175f0da15bd9e1cb5525e16319ce91fcc","tid":180490,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T08:16:13.000Z","msg":"台灣政黨輪替<br />\n後生仔 無罪<br />\n<br />\n香港777票<br />\n暴動坐3年"}]}